This is a matlab demo code for the algorithm described in the following paper:

Convolutional deep belief networks for scalable unsupervised learning of hierarchical representations.
Honglak Lee, Roger Grosse, Rajesh Ranganath, and Andrew Y. Ng.
In Proceedings of the 26th International Conference on Machine Learning (ICML), 2009. 


Copyright by Honglak Lee



Quick instruction: 
In matlab, run the following demo code

demo_train



If you use this code, please cite the following papers:

